gy five term exact sequence in the classical case over a field.\nCrossed pair algebras defined relative to a suitable notion of Q-equivariant\nGalois extension of commutative rings lead to a comparison of the theory with\nthe appropriate group cohomology groups and with the corresponding abelian\ngroup of classes of crossed pairs defined relative to the data. A number of\nexamples illustrating the theory are included.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Dec 2015 21:15:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Feb 2017 08:12:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-11"}
