ular, we demonstrate that the 3D model can qualitatively explain\ndeviations from the standard solar model found by helioseismology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Dec 2015 23:10:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-27"}
