o extend the scope of the ME to more\nsophisticated scenarios, beyond the simplest alpha-parameterization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Dec 2015 10:57:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Jun 2016 11:33:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 29 Sep 2016 08:21:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-26"}
